This paper discusses the use of machine learning to improve planning, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The focus on learning and improving system performance also suggests that it could be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG). The use of heuristics and search-based planning suggests that it could also be categorized under robotics (cs.RO) and software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper specifically mentions planning as a complementary approach, suggesting that it could also be categorized under planning (cs.PL).
